    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1952-07-23T14:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1952-07-23T14:00:00-05:00" n="68"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d68">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00/7–2352: Telegram</note>
                <head>No. 68<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France (<persName corresp="#p_DUNNJC1"
                            type="from">Dunn</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Department of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d68fn1">Repeated to London, Bonn, Rome, Brussels, The Hague,
                        and Luxembourg.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">confidential</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1952-07-23T20:00:00+01:00"
                            >July 23, 1952—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>522. Re <gloss target="#t_Embtel1">Embtel</gloss> 491, July 22, rptd London 88,
                    Bonn 66.<note n="2" xml:id="d68fn2">Not printed; it transmitted the text of a
                        French draft proposal on a European Political Authority substantially along
                        the lines reported in <ref target="#d62">Document 62</ref>.
                        (740.00/7–2252)</note> Subject is European political community.</p>
                <pb facs="0180" n="132" xml:id="pg_132"/>
                <p>Italian Emb informs us that in last night’s talk with <persName
                        corresp="#p_DEGASPERIA1">De Gasperi</persName>, <persName
                        corresp="#p_SCHUMANR1">Schuman</persName> accepted all major Italian
                    amendments mentioned para 3a through 3c <gloss target="#t_Reftel1"
                        >reftel</gloss>, and that common French-Italian proposal on European
                    political authority will be presented to six ministers probably tomorrow
                    afternoon. <persName corresp="#p_DEGASPERIA1">De Gasperi</persName> also saw
                        <persName corresp="#p_ADENAUERK1">Adenauer</persName> this morning, and was
                    very impressed with firm stand which Germans intend to take on importance moving
                    rapidly ahead to create common political authority. <persName
                        corresp="#p_ADENAUERK1">Adenauer</persName> was also as strongly opposed as
                    ever to use of Council of Europe Assembly.</p>
                <p>Our source seemed very encouraged by these developments. He believed that solid
                    French-German-Italian front can be maintained on this issue at tomorrow’s
                    (Thursday’s) meeting. Only serious difficulty he foresees will be Dutch effort
                    to keep this matter completely off ministers agenda on grounds that in absence
                    Dutch Government, <persName corresp="#p_STIKKERDU1">Stikker</persName> can not
                    take any commitments.</p>
                <p>
                    <persName corresp="#p_DEGASPERIA1">De Gasperi</persName> expressed himself as
                    strongly in favor close United States association with work of <persName
                        corresp="#p_SCHUMANR1">Schuman</persName> Plan Assembly on political
                    authority. <persName corresp="#p_DEGASPERIA1">De Gasperi</persName> discussed
                    this question also with <persName corresp="#p_ADENAUERK1">Adenauer</persName>,
                    who agreed entirely. <persName corresp="#p_DEGASPERIA1">De Gasperi</persName>
                    will probably make proposal in sense para 3d <gloss target="#t_Reftel1"
                        >reftel</gloss> when French-Italian proposal on political community is
                    discussed by ministers.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_DUNNJC1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Dunn</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
